title: WWF HARDCORE (2001) VHSRIP

WWF HARDCORE (WWF HOME VIDEO)
VHS RIP
TV-14
2001
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1444339/

Welcome to the world of anything goes. Barbed wire-wrapped baseball bats, steel cages, tacks & chairs are just some of the tools these artists of brutality use to take the sport to extremes the Federation and its fans have never witnessed before. These Superstars have become legends through their bodily sacrifices. If we said they didn't get hurt, we'd be lying. Like it hard? Then you'll friggin' love this, man!

*All of these events actually took place and are not re-enactments
